              li.product-view__display
                img(src="../images/products/driedMango2.png", alt="Dried Mango from philippines")
          .product-view__card
            .product-view__cta.mt-5.product-view__mobile
              button.button.button--secondary Prev
              button.button.button--secondary Next
            .product-view__header
              h3 Dried Mango 
                br.product-view__separator
                | By Philippine Brand
              p Country of Origin: Phlippines
            .product-view__caution
              .product-view__caution-card
                img.product-view__icon(src="../images/ingredients-icon.png")
                .product-view__card-details
                  h4 Ingredients
                  p Mangoes, Sugar, Sulfur Dioxide (as a preservative)
              .product-view__caution-card
                img.product-view__icon(src="../images/allergy-icon.png")
                .product-view__card-details
                  h4 Allergy Info
                  p Contains Mangos
            .product-view__description
              h4 Item Description
              p As anyone who has visited the Philippines can attest, dried mangos are a staple snack in the country, and are produced from the famous mangos of the Philippines. These dried mangos are sweet, chewy, and retain the moisture and flavor of the fruit when fresh. These dried mango also contain high fibre content, which is what gives the mango its very chewy texture. The combination of its taste and the texture makes this treat addictive to munch on. Take a pack with you and enjoy tropical mangos anywhere you go!
